# 🏥 MediCare — Hospital Management System

A complete Hospital Management System built with **Laravel 12**, featuring patient appointment booking, doctor management, Stripe payment integration, PDF generation, and role-based access control.

---

## 📸 Project Overview

MediCare is a full-featured hospital management system where patients can browse doctors, book appointments, and pay consultation fees online. Doctors can manage their appointments and write digital prescriptions. Admins have complete control over the system through a dedicated admin panel.

---

## ✨ Features

### 👤 Patient Side
- Register & Login
- Browse Doctors by Department
- Search Doctors by Name
- Filter Doctors by Department
- View Doctor Profile
- Book Appointment (with double-booking prevention)
- Pay Consultation Fee online (Stripe)
- View My Appointments with Status
- View & Download Prescription (PDF)
- Download Payment Receipt (PDF)

### 👨‍⚕️ Doctor Side
- Doctor Dashboard (stats overview)
- View All Appointments
- Update Appointment Status (Pending/Confirmed/Completed/Cancelled)
- Write Digital Prescriptions
- Add Multiple Medicines per Prescription

### 👨‍💼 Admin Panel
- Admin Dashboard (doctors, departments, appointments, revenue stats)
- Manage Departments (Add/Edit/Delete)
- Manage Doctors (Add/Edit/Delete with photo upload)
- View All Appointments
- Payment Reports (total revenue)
- View All Users

### 💳 Payment
- Stripe Payment Integration
- Test & Live mode support
- Payment receipt generation (PDF)
- Payment status tracking

### 📄 PDF Generation
- Prescription PDF download
- Payment Receipt PDF download

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Technology | Usage |
|---|---|
| Laravel 12 | Backend Framework |
| PHP 8.2 | Programming Language |
| MySQL | Database |
| Bootstrap 5 | Frontend Styling |
| Stripe | Payment Gateway |
| barryvdh/laravel-dompdf | PDF Generation |
| XAMPP | Local Development Server |

---

## 👥 User Roles

| Role | Access |
|---|---|
| **Patient** | Browse doctors, book appointments, pay, download prescriptions |
| **Doctor** | Manage appointments, write prescriptions |
| **Admin** | Full system control |

---

## 🗄️ Database Structure

| Table | Description |
|---|---|
| `users` | All users (role: patient/doctor/admin) |
| `departments` | Hospital departments (Cardiology, Dental, etc.) |
| `doctors` | Doctor profiles linked to users |
| `appointments` | Patient bookings with date/time/status |
| `prescriptions` | Doctor prescriptions with medicines (JSON) |
| `payments` | Payment records with Stripe transaction IDs |

---

## ⚙️ Installation & Setup

### **Requirements**
- PHP 8.2+
- Composer
- MySQL
- Node.js & npm
- XAMPP (or any local server)
- Stripe Account (for payments)

---

### **Step 1: Clone the Repository**
```bash
git clone https://github.com/khanjee56/hospital-management.git
cd hospital-management
```

### **Step 2: Install Dependencies**
```bash
composer install
npm install
npm run build
```

### **Step 3: Environment Setup**
```bash
cp .env.example .env
php artisan key:generate
```

### **Step 4: Configure Database**
Open `.env` and update:
```env
DB_DATABASE=hospital_management
DB_USERNAME=root
DB_PASSWORD=
```

### **Step 5: Configure Stripe**
```env
STRIPE_KEY=pk_test_your_publishable_key
STRIPE_SECRET=sk_test_your_secret_key
```

### **Step 6: Configure Gmail (For Email)**
```env
MAIL_MAILER=smtp
MAIL_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
MAIL_PORT=587
MAIL_USERNAME=youremail@gmail.com
MAIL_PASSWORD=your_app_password
MAIL_ENCRYPTION=tls
MAIL_FROM_ADDRESS=youremail@gmail.com
MAIL_FROM_NAME="MediCare Hospital"
```

### **Step 7: Run Migrations & Seed Data**
```bash
php artisan migrate:fresh --seed
```

### **Step 8: Create Storage Link**
```bash
php artisan storage:link
```

### **Step 9: Run the Project**
```bash
php artisan serve
```

Open browser → `http://localhost:8000`

